            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:fddfe334-f7ff-4133-9368-9e6b008eeeb9</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/green_manufacturing/~3/9WicrHV6gG8/Toyota-president-outlines-goals</link>
