            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:aa892c28-68e7-4ec4-8d82-9e6900d4f5ae</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/green_manufacturing/~3/VFZNyizrdgg/EPA-GHG-permitting-requirements</link>
