            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:777865b1-d163-4e6d-8f4e-9e54009fa5c0</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/green_manufacturing/~3/4srNATC_xVg/Akzo-Nobel-environmental-management</link>
