			&lt;td valign="top"&gt;
				Working alongside Chichibu&amp;#39;s city enhancement plan through local citizen cooperation, conduct studies to increase use of electromotive mobility opportunities and its convenience by renting out Monpal to citizens and tourists.&lt;br /&gt;
				&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;
