	&lt;strong&gt;[Solar-powered charging station]&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
	Located inside Honda&amp;#39;s Wako Headquarters Campus in Saitama Prefecture, this charging station features a solar-powered generating system manufactured by Honda Soltec. Honda will use the station in combination with advanced communications &amp;amp; telematics to test a wide variety of program objectives.&lt;br /&gt;
