            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:ee35b2fa-3551-457b-8f77-9e17006c1c95</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/green_manufacturing/~3/tFtrGKHe-28/Nissan-production-LEAF-Japan</link>
